  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Carriers are military ships designed to deploy large
  numbers of star fighters. They typically have weak weaponry, but instead =
have
  multiple fighter bays.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>To build Carriers you must first research them in the
  Weapons tech tree.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Carriers can be built 50% larger than your current maxi=
mum
  ship construction size.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>They should always be escorted with other military ship=
s.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
